<p>therefore that when numbers are so limited officers have to take their turn, and while your son's work was of a high order he was only one of many whose work was equally meritorious.  Had he lived he would most certainly have been included in the last half yearly list or this one. He knew the circumstances very well &ndash; and I am sure was not at all worried.</p>
